l.png?m=1582875070", "title": "Chrome", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/chrome", "topics": 2086, "footer": "", "header": "Google Chrome is a browser that combines a minimal design with sophisticated technology to make the web faster, safer, and easier.", "title_alternative": "Chrome", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/92cc/2275/92_mini.png?m=1582875070", "stars": 1080, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 92, "parent_node_name": "browsers"}, "member": {"id": 560653, "username": "NIIIIIIIIIICE", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/NIIIIIIIIIICE", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d1b6/cfba/560653_mini.png?m=1717319368", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d1b6/cfba/560653_normal.png?m=1717319368", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d1b6/cfba/560653_large.png?m=1717319368", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d1b6/cfba/560653_xlarge.png?m=1717319368", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d1b6/cfba/560653_xlarge.png?m=1717319368", "created": 1635980254, "last_modified": 1717319368}, "last_reply_by": "hanqian", "last_touched": 1717379374, "title": "Chrome 将在明天推行均有争议的 Manifest V3 了 大量 Manifest V2 扩展将被禁用", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1046137", "created": 1717319752, "deleted": 0, "content": "最早从 2024 年 6 月的 Chrome 127 开始，我们将开始停用 Chrome 的不稳定版本（开发者版、Canary 版和 Beta 版）中的 Manifest V2 扩展程序。受此变化影响的用户会在浏览器中看到 Manifest V2 扩展程序自动停用，并且无法再从 Chrome 应用商店安装 Manifest V2 扩展程序。此外，Manifest V2 扩展程序在 Chrome 应用商店中将不再拥有“精选”徽章（如果目前已有该徽章）。\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n原文： https://developer.chrome.com/blog/resuming-the-transition-to-mv3?hl=zh-cn\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n检查了我工作生活会用到那些浏览器扩展，大部分都是 manifest V2 ，尤其是国内的😓看来又快要度过一个混乱时期了，已经禁止 Chrome 自动更新，看看情况再说。", "content_rendered": "<p>最早从 2024 年 6 月的 Chrome 127 开始，我们将开始停用 Chrome 的不稳定版本（开发者版、Canary 版和 Beta 版）中的 Manifest V2 扩展程序。受此变化影响的用户会在浏览器中看到 Manifest V2 扩展程序自动停用，并且无法再从 Chrome 应用商店安装 Manifest V2 扩展程序。此外，Manifest V2 扩展程序在 Chrome 应用商店中将不再拥有“精选”徽章（如果目前已有该徽章）。</p>\n<p>原文： <a href=\"https://developer.chrome.com/blog/resuming-the-transition-to-mv3?hl=zh-cn\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://developer.chrome.com/blog/resuming-the-transition-to-mv3?hl=zh-cn</a></p>\n<p>检查了我工作生活会用到那些浏览器扩展，大部分都是 manifest V2 ，尤其是国内的😓看来又快要度过一个混乱时期了，已经禁止 Chrome 自动更新，看看情况再说。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1717319752, "replies": 65, "id": 1046137}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/979d/472a/213_large.png?m=1635464761", "name": "suzhou", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/979d/472a/213_normal.png?m=1635464761", "title": "苏州", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/suzhou", "topics": 126, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Suzhou", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/979d/472a/213_mini.png?m=1635464761", "stars": 310, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 213, "parent_node_name": "cn"}, "member": {"id": 494632, "username": "bthulu", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/bthulu", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c87484c1062f990c6ef9e1a9c27bdc60?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c87484c1062f990c6ef9e1a9c27bdc60?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c87484c1062f990c6ef9e1a9c27bdc60?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1592099578, "last_modified": 1669598980}, "last_reply_by": "Kidlet7", "last_touched": 1717381461, "title": "苏州一小区里有人组织聚众赌博, 赌博窝点附近几个出入口 24 小时有人站岗放哨, 我要怎么才能无伤举报掉?", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1046194", "created": 1717373141, "deleted": 0, "content": "我家就在旁边, 每天看着来来回回那么多人, 好怕他们赌红了眼打起来.\r\n\r\n小区旁边就有警务室, 貌似他们在装瞎子. 之前我装修的时候, 外立面稍微动了一点, 物业就过来了, 现在别人赌博赌的飞起, 物业一句话也没有.\r\n\r\n用国内手机举报我肯定是不敢了, 现在又没有不记名手机卡, 还有啥办法匿名举报吗? 据说匿名举报根本没人管的, 也不知道是不是真的.", "content_rendered": "<p>我家就在旁边, 每天看着来来回回那么多人, 好怕他们赌红了眼打起来.</p>\n<p>小区旁边就有警务室, 貌似他们在装瞎子. 之前我装修的时候, 外立面稍微动了一点, 物业就过来了, 现在别人赌博赌的飞起, 物业一句话也没有.</p>\n<p>用国内手